{"tid":412040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣都好易睇錯野","createTime":"2017-09-24T10:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T10:18:31.000Z","uid":147727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee52cc5fc888c7432f875f9c601a7689fbc3061","tid":412040,"uid":147727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日晏晝就去吉野家食下午茶啦<br />\n我就叫左個普通茶餐加杯可樂2$<br />\n係等佢收錢個陣無聊就周圍望下<br />\n見到原來特飲+3就有 好過飲無氣可樂啦<br />\n跟住我即刻好急咁問佢<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收銀條友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔該想問下呢個巨乳提子特飲係咪加3$炸？可唔可以幫我轉一轉岩岩杯可樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條友呆左咁望住我 隔離同後面d人即刻靜撚曬望住我<br />\n我先知自己講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個一下真係柒到想即刻跑走<br />\n最後我急急腳拎住個餐行到最後角落位食算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底有冇人會同我一樣睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zxl8dr4m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzxl8dr4m&h=45740231&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}